                    "name": "field_1_1",
                    "label": "Important Notes",
                    "type": "notes",
                    "placeholder": null,
                    "description": "<p><strong><u>Important Notes:</u></strong></p><ol><li>Please complete the Data Correction Request Form and ensure that your personal data provided herein is genuine and accurate.</li><li>Your request may not be processed if the information/document provided is incomplete.</li><li>Third Party Requestor is to be present at the branch / office to submit this form and for verification of information and documents required.</li><li>The supporting document(s) required in this form must be provided. We will respond within 21 days of receipt of the completed form with accompanying documents.</li><li>If you have any queries / need any guidance in filling-up this form, you may contact our</li></ol><p>\t\t\t<strong><em>Customer Service Department at the contact details below:</em></strong></p><p><strong><em>\t\t\tHead, Customer Service Department, Bank Muamalat  Malaysia Berhad</em></strong></p><p><strong><em>\t\t\tAddress\t\t: 19th Floor, Menara Bumiputra, Jalan Melaka, 51000 Kuala Lumpur</em></strong></p><p><strong><em>\t\t\tTelephone\t: 1-300-88-8787 (Local), +603-26005500 (International)</em></strong></p><p><strong><em>\t\t\tEmail\t\t\t: feedback@muamalat.com.my</em></strong></p>",
